@JWoldense @rstats_tweets If you want to do floating point comparison in #RStats, you can use all.equal.numeric() which uses sqrt(.Machine$double.eps)
> seq(-2.6, 2.6, by = 0.1)[47] == 2
[1] FALSE
> all.equal.numeric(seq(-2.6, 2.6, by = 0.1)[47], 2)
[1] TRUE
See ?all.equal.numeric for more details
